{
  "stem": "1929.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, that's, that's when-- you know, that's when-- and what they would do is it would be like-- you know, they would impose a fine, so many million slaughters or something like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, it was up to the council to collect the money and turn it over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would force laborers to come in, you know, to have people send them to labor camps and things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was up to the Jewish council to do-- they, they basically, they did most of the-- most of the dirty work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were, per se, there were not too many Germans in the ghetto in those years, as such.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mostly there were Polish policemen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had come back in about-- I would think they were probably 1940, yeah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came back when the ghetto was established.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were living already in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was wounded in the war, quite severely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he really, they were going to shoot him, but he talked German to them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Knowing how to speak German saved his life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he was-- when they were going to shoot him, he said, [SPEAKING GERMAN], volks Deutsche.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm a German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And because he spoke German so well, they believed him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took him off to the hospital, and he spent like, six months or something in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was burned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had wounds in his leg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he came back into the ghetto where we were living in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the first day he came back, you know, we had no expectation that when he would arrive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he came in, and we were all absolutely thrilled and--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, he-- there was a mail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was able to write to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
